    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The discipline of combining vocal or instrumental sounds to produce beauty of form, harmony, melody, rhythm, expressive content, etc.; musical composition, performance, analysis, etc., as a subject of study; the occupation or profession of musicians.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
